date=18 November 2018}}</ref>\n| Race_No = 9\n| Season_No = 20\n| Location = [[Red Bull Ring]]<br />[[Spielberg, Styria|Spielberg]], [[Styria]], Austria\n| Course = Permanent racing facility \n| Course_mi = 2.683\n| Course_km = 4.318\n| Distance_laps = 71\n| Distance_mi = 190.420\n| Distance_km = 306.452\n| Weather = Partly cloudy\n| Attendance = 145,000<ref>{{cite news|title=F1 reveals overall rise in 2017 attendance|url=https://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/361717/f1-reveals-eight-per-cent-rise-in-2017-attendance/|website=Gpupdate.net|date=8 December 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171209011037/https://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/361717/f1-reveals-eight-per-cent-rise-in-2017-attendance/|archive-date=9 December 2017}}</ref>\n| Pole_Driver = [[Valtteri Bottas]]\n| Pole_Team = [[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]\n| Pole_Time = 1:04.251\n| Pole_Country = FIN\n| Fast_Driver = [[Lewis Hamilton]]\n| Fast_Team = [[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]\n| Fast_Time = 1:07.411\n| Fast_Lap = 69 \n| Fast_Country = GBR\n| First_Driver = [[Valtteri Bottas]]\n| First_Team = [[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]\n| First_Country = FIN\n| Second_Driver = {{nowrap|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Sebastian Vettel]]}}\n| Second_Team = [[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n| Third_Driver = {{nowrap|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Daniel Ricciardo]]}}\n| Third_Team = {{nowrap|[[Red Bull Racing]]-[[TAG Heuer]]}}\n| Lapchart = {{F1Laps2017|AUT}}\n|Previous_round=2017 Azerbaijan Grand Prix}}\n\nThe '''2017 Austrian Grand Prix''' (formally known as the '''Formula 1 Gro\u00dfer Preis von \u00d6sterreich 2017''') was a [[Formula One]] [[auto racing|motor race]] that took place on 9 July 2017 at the [[Red Bull Ring]] in [[Spielberg, Styria|Spielberg]], Austria. The race, which was contested over seventy-one laps, was the ninth round of the [[2017 FIA Formula One World Championship]], and marked the 31st running of the [[Austrian Grand Prix]] and the 30th time it had been held as a round of the Formula One World Championship since the series inception in {{F1|1950}}, every time at Spielberg using the current or former variations of this circuit.\n\n[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]] driver [[Sebastian Vettel]] entered the round as the [[List of Formula One World Drivers' Champions|championship leader]], with a 14-point advantage over [[Lewis Hamilton]], and extended it to 20 points. [[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]] led Ferrari by 24 points in the [[List of Formula One World Constructors' Champions|Constructors' standings]] at the start of the round, and extended it to 33 points.\n\n==Classification==\n===Qualifying===\n{|class=wikitable style=\"font-size:85%\"\n!rowspan=2|{{Tooltip|Pos.|Qualifying position}}\n!rowspan=2|{{Tooltip|Car<br>no.|Number}}\n!rowspan=2|Driver\n!rowspan=2|Constructor\n!colspan=3| {{nowrap|Qualifying times}}\n!rowspan=2|{{Tooltip|Final<br>grid|Final grid position}}\n|-\n!Q1\n!Q2\n!Q3\n|-\n!1\n|align=\"center\"|77\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Valtteri Bottas]]\n|[[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]] \n|1:05.760\n|'''1:04.316'''\n|'''1:04.251'''\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n!2\n|align=\"center\"|5\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Sebastian Vettel]]\n|[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|1:05.585\n|1:04.772\n|1:04.293\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|-\n!3\n|align=\"center\"|44\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Lewis Hamilton]]\n|[[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]\n|'''1:05.064'''\n|1:04.800\n|1:04.424\n|align=\"center\"|8{{ref|Q1|1}}\n|-\n!4\n|align=\"center\"|7\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Kimi R\u00e4ikk\u00f6nen]]\n|[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|1:05.148\n|1:05.004\n|1:04.779\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|-\n!5\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Daniel Ricciardo]]\n|{{nowrap|[[Red Bull Racing]]-[[TAG Heuer]]}}\n|1:05.854\n|1:05.161\n|1:04.896\n|align=\"center\"|4\n|-\n!6\n|align=\"center\"|33\n|{{flagicon|NED}} [[Max Verstappen]]\n|{{nowrap|[[Red Bull Racing]]-[[TAG Heuer]]}}\n|1:05.779\n|1:04.948\n|1:04.983\n|align=\"center\"|5\n|-\n!7\n|align=\"center\"|8\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Roma